http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Rs.-6-lakh-stolen-from-parked-car/article13997353.ece

A sum of Rs. 6 lakh has been stolen from a car parked on M.G. Road in the town on Wednesday.Miscreants broke the window panes of the car belonging to Suresh, a farmer from Sugatur in Kolar, and made away with the cash kept in it. Town police are investigating.